high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter with the coffee maker, then turn right to face the counter with the toaster on it.
Pick up the pan from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and go toward the door, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside, and take it back out.
Turn around and go forward toward the wall, then turn right to face the white table.
Put the pan on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the white table.

high_descs: Take a small step forward then turn right and walk to the counter then turn right.
Pick up the frying pan that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the door then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall in front of you then turn right.
Put the pan on the table in front of you near the corner that's nearest you.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.  Turn right again so you are facing the toaster.
Pick up the frying pan in front of the toaster.
Turn right and walk to the door.  Turn left and face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door and place the frying pan on the top shelf in the refrigerator and close the refrigerator door again.  Open the refrigerator door and remove the frying pan from the top shelf, then close the refrigerator door.
Turn completely around, walk to the wall, turn to the right so you are facing the white table.
Place the frying pan on the table in front of the stool.
anns.task_desc: Chill the frying pan and put it on the table.
